          – Nachträgliche Notiz unten rechts von dritter Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>Prot.</abbr><expan>Protokoll</expan></choice> <date when="1877-05-31">31. V. 77</date>. <choice><abbr>N</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 1156.</orig> </note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
